<h1>To finish creating your account you need to set up 2-factor verification</h1>
<h2 class="step">Step 1 of 2</h2>

<p>Download the <strong>Google Authenticator</strong> app on your smart phone. You can download it from the App Store or Google Play. Then select <strong>Set up account</strong>.</p>

<div class="qrcode">
  <p><strong>Scan the QR code below into the app</strong></p>
  <img alt="QR code" src="/users/shared_secrets/code.png?nocache=<%= rand %>" />
</div>


<ul class="list-unstyled sub-link-list">
  <li><%= link_to 'Generate a new code', users_shared_secret_path, method: :delete, class:'UIK-link' %></li>
  <li><%= link_to 'Can\'t scan it?', code_users_shared_secrets_path, class:'UIK-link' %></li>
</ul>


<div class="form-ctas mt-2">
  <%= link_to 'Next >', new_users_shared_secret_path, role: :button, class:'UIK-button btn btn-primary' %>
</div>
